The Greffon Catalog contains docker-compose templates and metadata for
third-party applications. Each catalog entry references an upstream
application (Plausible, Ghost, Nextcloud, GlitchTip, OpenClaw, FreqTrade,
etc.) which retains its own license and copyright. The Apache 2.0 license
in this repository applies to the catalog templates and tooling, not to the
applications they deploy.
